summary:
Selfmade entrepreneur.
Co-founder and Head of Growth of the immigration platform Hello Move.

For over 15 years I have worked in marketing communications and advertising in Russia. But I wanted more and I started my own business. My first brainchild was an online organic soap shop, then I founded a web and design studio. But at the age of 35, I decided to take a chance and abandoned everything I had, to go to the Netherlands to create a startup.

With my huge pool of unique knowledge that can help many people move to another country, my business partner and I decided to create the Hello Move migration platform. And we have created a unique system for going through the migration process on our own without the need to use a lawyer. Isn't that excellent? Huh?
